{"tid":662433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"四 川 省 安 排 施 襲 者 向 陳 浩 暉 道 歉","createTime":"2018-05-12T12:11:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-13T18:01:21.000Z","uid":41404,"like":2,"dislike":64,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"7c2417f2f2e784712b3f3be954f363c7a83476db","tid":662433,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T12:11:20.000Z","msg":"香港有線記者陳浩暉，在四川都江堰採訪地震十周年悼念活動時，被兩個男人毆打。<br />\n<br />\n四川省當局安排兩人傍晚時向陳浩暉道歉。他們自稱是都江堰居民，一人指鄰居在汶川地震中死亡，另一人指當年房子倒塌、家人受傷，看見陳浩暉拍攝時觸動傷疤，覺得非常難過而變得激動，並非是見記者採訪而施襲。他們面帶笑容向陳浩暉鞠躬，表示真誠對不起，非常不好意思。<br />\n<br />\n陳浩暉表示接受道歉。<br />\n<br />\n曾經指未能跟進施襲者身分的都江堰外宣辦，主任劉洪對事件感到非常抱歉，真誠向香港傳媒及陳浩暉本人致歉，並會加強向公眾宣傳配合傳媒工作。對於當局會否向施襲者循法律追究，她指會根據調查再作決定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1396054-20180512.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1396054-20180512.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=6nIkTrmhJYfV7Y6X%2BYq6VAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=26c29981\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1396054-20180512.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=ea404fc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1396054-20180512.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"4d84f05586c3eddffdff790d5b833993ff8cbe6d","tid":662433,"uid":25858,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T12:12:13.000Z","msg":"被安排<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2ca695f12dc016e56dd2cc3d28cbdf7a850494b","tid":662433,"uid":26752,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T12:14:19.000Z","msg":"唔怪得CCTVB會報啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過係咪真係個兩個人呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4633ffcfaf866d398e26d50af064347528a991a","tid":662433,"uid":2772,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T12:14:21.000Z","m